ZH: 时间过得很快，一切都成为过眼烟云。
EN: Time passes by quickly, everything becomes a passing cloud.

ZH: 生活中的困难都会过眼烟云。
EN: The difficulties in life will all become passing clouds.

ZH: 成功和荣誉都是过眼烟云。
EN: Success and honor are all passing clouds.

ZH: 只有真正的友谊才能经得起时间的考验，不会过眼烟云。
EN: Only true friendship can stand the test of time and not just be a passing cloud.

ZH: 记住，物质财富都是过眼烟云。
EN: Remember, material wealth is just a passing cloud.

ZH: 人生的苦难和痛苦终究会过眼烟云。
EN: The hardships and pain in life will eventually become passing clouds.

ZH: 青春就像过眼烟云，转瞬即逝。
EN: Youth is like a passing cloud, fleeting.

ZH: 爱情有时会是过眼烟云，有时会永不磨灭。
EN: Love can sometimes be a passing cloud, sometimes it can be everlasting.

ZH: 忧愁和快乐都是过眼烟云。
EN: Sorrow and happiness are all passing clouds.

ZH: 当下的烦恼其实都是过眼烟云。
EN: The worries of the present are actually just passing clouds.

ZH: 世上的名利都是过眼烟云。
EN: The fame and fortune in the world are all passing clouds.

ZH: 这场风波终究会过眼烟云。
EN: This storm will eventually become a passing cloud.

ZH: 真正的智慧会超越一切过眼烟云。
EN: True wisdom will transcend all passing clouds.

ZH: 我不会被一时的挫折打败，这只是过眼烟云。
EN: I will not be defeated by temporary setbacks, they are just passing clouds.

ZH: 所有的过往都是过眼烟云。
EN: All past events are passing clouds.

ZH: 修行者懂得放下名利，因为它们都是过眼烟云。
EN: Practitioners understand how to let go of fame and fortune because they are all passing clouds.

ZH: 人生之路上的风风雨雨终将变成过眼烟云。
EN: The ups and downs in the journey of life will eventually become passing clouds.

ZH: 在时间面前，一切都是过眼烟云。
EN: In front of time, everything is a passing cloud.

ZH: 父母对孩子的爱永不会是过眼烟云。
EN: The love of parents for their children will never be a passing cloud.
